window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Isaac sets off ahead of the rest of his family with Kat and his mana beasts. No matter how much he'd practiced with immortal mana before venturing into the immortal world hadnâ€™t prepared him for it, and his first bumbling steps into the new world have him collared and sold to a brothel.</p> <p>Those who did this to him will pay dearly for underestimating him. Isaac plots his escape and the new path in cultivation as he makes plans to break through to his fifth ring and seek revenge.</p>"; 
